headline: 3 Top Fertilizer Stocks to Watch From a Promising Industry
summary: Favorable demand in major markets for crop nutrients, backed by the strength in global agriculture markets, should enable the Zacks Fertilizers industry to thrive. NTR, CF and ICL should benefit from supportive industry fundamentals.
